author: Second Wind
description:
On this week's episode of Unpacked, Nick digs into the success of Clair Obscur: Expedition 33, and how its developer Sandfall Interactive and publisher Kepler could be a model for future success across the industry.

From the team behind The Escapist, we're excited to introduce you to our new employee-owned and fully independent outlet, Second Wind.
